 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Ek vrek oor &#8216;n cremoratert. &nbsp;Ek besluit toe om die tert te maak na my skoonsus se smaak. Dis met &#8216;n hartseerhart dat ek moet se sy is oorlede voor sy die tert kon proe. &nbsp;Ek dra die tert op aan my skoonsus Joanita Engelbrecht. &nbsp;Wou so graag vir haar &#8216;n stukkie gevat het. Die lewe is kort. Maak die tert en eet hom! Dit is &#8216;n vermenging van cremora/subtiele sjokolade en &#8216;n marshmellow smaak. Dit is &#8216;n groot tert wat in &#8216;n losboompan gemaak word.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-768x1024.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6294\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3704.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-768x1024.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6295\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3720.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-768x1024.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6296\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/08/IMG_3748.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"></figure></div>",
